90
00:04:51,050 --> 00:04:52,830
That was true?

91
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,480
It's all true.

92
00:04:55,140 --> 00:04:56,390
Our department

93
00:04:57,620 --> 00:04:59,930
can't meet his standard now,

94
00:05:01,010 --> 00:05:02,940
but even when we're tired,

95
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:04,240
