96
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:09,230
Hey, let's just make this project work.

97
00:05:09,530 --> 00:05:10,640
Group Leader Song, come on.

98
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,560
OK.

99
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:13,360
Oh, sir.

100
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:19,470
Oh, Lee Jun and

101
