266
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:22,320
♪It's enough to have you here♪

267
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:25,550
♪I will guard your heart♪

268
00:16:26,060 --> 00:16:28,590
Whatever. It doesn't matter.

269
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:36,810
