to the one you like.

278
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:12,360
Best partners?

279
00:17:13,550 --> 00:17:15,130
Yes, what's wrong?

280
00:17:15,710 --> 00:17:16,800
You don't like this flavor?

281
00:17:17,570 --> 00:17:19,330
I'm fine, I'll pass.

282
00:17:21,290 --> 00:17:23,390
Wait a minute then.

283
00:17:25,260 --> 00:17:31,450
♪Stay your night♪

284
00:17:32,490 --> 00:17:33,460
Take this.

285
00:17:35,570 --> 00:17:37,120
