286
00:17:37,570 --> 00:17:41,250
I didn't receive it,
I'm giving it to you.

287
00:17:41,770 --> 00:17:43,680
This is my favorite candy

288
00:17:44,050 --> 00:17:46,270
for my favorite person.

289
00:17:47,310 --> 00:17:50,450
♪Even if we're not in a hurry♪

290
00:17:50,450 --> 00:17:53,680
Thank you. I will prepare
something for you next time.

291
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:55,070
OK.

292
00:18:19,820 --> 00:18:20,720
I know that.

293
00:18:23,990 --> 00:18:24,830
Wake-up Instinct.

294
00:18:25,580 --> 00:18:28,510
Do you also know you are trespassing?

295
00:18:38,920 --> 00:18:40,870
Wow, that was crazy.

296
00:18:40,870 --> 00:18:43,140
You looked sober when you were drunk!

297
00:18:43,310 --> 00:18:44,940
Why did you come to my place?

298
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:50,440
I didn't come to your place
because I was drunk.

299
00:18:52,980 --> 00:18:54,660
You know what you are talking about?

300
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:59,180
You came to my place all of a sudden.

301
00:18:59,440 --> 00:19:01,600
If it was not because you were drunk,

302
00:19:01,600 --> 00:19:03,710
could it be because
you came back from America?

303
00:19:05,370 --> 00:19:06,420
I think

304
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:08,420
you have some fantasies about America.

305
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,830
You are so into fantasies.

306
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:12,600
But you are driving me crazy!

307
00:19:14,110 --> 00:19:14,970
Hey!

308
00:19:15,620 --> 00:19:17,460
This is the American style.

309
00:19:20,380 --> 00:19:21,220
Oh...

310
00:19:22,550 --> 00:19:23,740
Your shampoo smells good.

311
00:19:25,010 --> 00:19:25,850
Where did you buy it?

312
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:27,680
Let me go.

313
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:29,220
And I'm a native Korean!

314
00:19:41,290 --> 00:19:46,700
The General Manager is pretty tough.

315
00:19:47,940 --> 00:19:48,780
Are you depressed?

316
00:19:50,820 --> 00:19:51,660
It's...

317
00:19:53,380 --> 00:19:55,560
It's tough.

318
00:20:01,020 --> 00:20:04,120
(This is normal
for a man in the morning.)

319
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,940
(But why isn't he saying anything?)

320
00:20:06,810 --> 00:20:08,640
(Is it because he's young?)

321
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:10,090
(Why is it so...)

322
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:12,360
(Ah! What are you thinking about?)

323
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:14,190
(Wait a moment.)

324
00:20:14,820 --> 00:20:16,640
(How can I stand up naturally?)

325
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:19,660
You are thinking too loud, you know?

326
00:20:23,680 --> 00:20:26,030
It's tough for both of us.

327
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:28,600
How about this?

328
00:20:34,420 --> 00:20:35,260
Help me with it.

329
00:20:36,360 --> 00:20:37,200
What?

330
00:20:38,270 --> 00:20:39,110
You...

331
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:44,960
What exactly are you talking about?

332
00:20:48,980 --> 00:20:49,820
You would

333
00:20:52,030 --> 00:20:54,580
ask someone to help you at this time?

334
00:20:56,840 --> 00:21:00,230
I mean, when you
have a physical reaction,

335
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:03,940
you would ask others to help you?

336
00:21:04,510 --> 00:21:07,160
Is this the way of life you pursue?

337
00:21:08,100 --> 00:21:09,820
Why is it getting bigger?

338
00:21:10,670 --> 00:21:14,030
Ah, I'm surprised about one thing.

339
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,420
What is it?

340
00:21:18,360 --> 00:21:20,000
You are still so cute

341
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:23,100
as a grown-up.

342
00:21:31,050 --> 00:21:33,520
Hello everyone,
I am Lee Jun from Zeus.

343
00:21:34,300 --> 00:21:36,240
Here comes the first question.

344
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:39,960
Why do you want to be an idol?

345
00:21:43,500 --> 00:21:45,380
Now that I have become an idol,

346
00:21:45,620 --> 00:21:48,350
I want someone to see me now.

347
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:51,230
Can you tell us who that person is?

348
00:21:51,380 --> 00:21:53,590
It's a secret.

349
00:21:55,330 --> 00:21:57,900
So who could that person be?

350
00:22:00,760 --> 00:22:02,300
I haven't seen him yet.

351
00:22:06,610 --> 00:22:08,510
It is about to start.

352
00:22:09,020 --> 00:22:10,630
The next question
is from Mr. Candy Melon.

353
00:22:11,480 --> 00:22:13,980
What is your ideal other half?

354
00:22:14,630 --> 00:22:16,340
Oh, ideal other half?

355
00:22:17,840 --> 00:22:19,210
This person must smell good.

356
00:22:19,920 --> 00:22:20,760
Smell?

357
00:22:21,260 --> 00:22:22,100
Yes.

358
00:22:22,810 --> 00:22:28,120
It must be a person
who can make me warm.

359
00:22:28,320 --> 00:22:30,900
When I'm with this person,

360
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:33,320
I will feel so warm inside.

361
00:22:35,260 --> 00:22:36,610
That's quite specific.

362
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:40,020
Are you talking about your first love?

363
00:22:43,950 --> 00:22:45,690
Ha, well...

364
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:54,330
♪Please let me know,
oh don't let me know♪

365
00:22:54,670 --> 00:23:00,340
♪No matter where I am,
once I smell the aroma♪

366
00:23:00,910 --> 00:23:03,790
♪I know it's you♪

367
00:23:03,820 --> 00:23:06,140
♪I'm like a fool♪

368
00:23:06,140 --> 00:23:09,620
♪But when I think of you♪

369
00:23:10,620 --> 00:23:12,870
♪There are no rules♪

370
00:23:12,870 --> 00:23:14,160
=Jun and Jun=

371
00:23:14,580 --> 00:23:16,620
People living in different environments

372
00:23:16,620 --> 00:23:18,670
also have different values.

373
00:23:18,670 --> 00:23:19,980
That's right.

374
00:23:19,980 --> 00:23:21,340
Those living in another country

375
00:23:21,340 --> 00:23:24,060
have very different values from ours.

376
00:23:24,660 --> 00:23:26,200
For your information,
the General Manager

377
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:27,320
will also come today.

378
00:23:27,710 --> 00:23:29,910
Maybe it's
the General Manager's preference.

379
00:23:30,610 --> 00:23:33,550
I'd rather work in the marketing team.

380
00:23:33,990 --> 00:23:35,440
He said you would see

381
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:38,190
that disgusting Chim On out there.

382
00:23:38,660 --> 00:23:39,690
That's right.

383
00:23:39,690 --> 00:23:41,710
Maybe our little Jun
is smarter than imagined.

384
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:43,540
Does it smell good?

385
00:23:44,120 --> 00:23:45,020
Don't!
